init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is the story of the rebirth of magic in a world where it has long been forgotten.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story is told through the eyes of the main character, a young man named Riku.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is the son of a powerful mage, and has been trained in the art of magic from a young age.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is the only one of his kind to have been born in a hundred years.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story begins when Riku is a young boy, and follows him as he grows up and learns to control his magic.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is sent to a school for mages, where he meets many other students his age.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is able to learn spells that take others years to master in a matter of days.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is also able to cast spells that no one else can.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a very powerful mage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Riku is also very skilled in the art of hand to hand combat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is able to take on many enemies at once and defeat them with ease.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is a very evil person and is the complete opposite of Riku.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is able to cast spells that Riku has never seen before.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story continues as Riku grows up and is forced to make decisions that will change the world forever.
